  <data name="Priv_S1_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>01 Overview</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S1_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>FinanceApp is a personal finance management application. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data with care, transparency, and respect. This policy applies to all users of FinanceApp and describes how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our service.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S1_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>By using FinanceApp you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of the application.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S1_Highlight" xml:space="preserve"><value>Short version: We collect only what we need to run the app. We never sell your data. You control your data.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>02 Information We Collect</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>We collect the minimum information necessary to provide the service:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_AccountHdr" xml:space="preserve"><value>Account information</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_FinancialHdr" xml:space="preserve"><value>Financial data you enter</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_TechHdr" xml:space="preserve"><value>Technical data</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>03 How We Use Your Data</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Your data is used exclusively to operate and improve FinanceApp. Specifically, we use it to:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>We do not use your financial data for advertising, profiling, or selling to third parties.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>04 Storage &amp; Security</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>We take security seriously and have implemented multiple layers of protection:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>05 Data Retention</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Your data is retained for as long as your account remains active. When you delete your account:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can request deletion of specific records at any time from within the application using the delete actions on each record.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>06 Your Rights &amp; Controls</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>You have full control over your data within FinanceApp:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>If you need assistance exercising any of these rights, please contact us using the information in Section 10.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S7_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>07 Third-Party Services</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S7_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>FinanceApp loads the following third-party resources to power the interface:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S7_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>These services receive only your IP address and browser headers as part of standard HTTP requests. No financial data is transmitted to any of these services. We do not use analytics tools, advertising networks, or any tracking pixels.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S8_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>08 Cookies</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S8_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>FinanceApp uses a minimal set of cookies, all strictly necessary for the application to function:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S8_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>We do not use advertising cookies, tracking cookies, or any cookies from third-party ad networks.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_TableCookie" xml:space="preserve"><value>Cookie</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_TablePurpose" xml:space="preserve"><value>Purpose</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_TableDuration" xml:space="preserve"><value>Duration</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S9_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>09 Changes to This Policy</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S9_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>We may update this policy from time to time to reflect changes in the application or applicable law. When we do:</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S9_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Continued use of FinanceApp after a policy update constitutes acceptance of the revised policy. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S10_H2" xml:space="preserve"><value>10 Contact Us</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S10_P1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Have questions, concerns, or a data request? We're here to help.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S10_P2" xml:space="preserve"><value>We aim to respond to all privacy-related inquiries within 5 business days.</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_A1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Name, email address, and password (stored as a secure hash — we never store plain-text passwords)</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_A2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Optional profile photo you upload</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_A3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Subscription plan and assignment date</value></data>
