  <data name="Priv_S2_T1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Authentication tokens and session identifiers</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S2_T2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Anti-forgery tokens for security</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Authenticate you and maintain a secure session</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Display your financial records, summaries, and budgets</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Generate Excel exports of your data on demand</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Serve uploaded receipt and document files back to you</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L5" xml:space="preserve"><value>Send security-related emails (e.g. password reset) when you request them</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S3_L6" xml:space="preserve"><value>Improve application performance and fix bugs</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Passwords are hashed using ASP.NET Core Identity's industry-standard algorithm (PBKDF2 with HMAC-SHA256) — the original password is never stored</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Authentication uses secure, HTTP-only session cookies with anti-forgery token validation on every state-changing request</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Database is isolated per deployment — your data is not commingled with other users' data without access controls</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Uploaded files are stored server-side and accessed only by the authenticated owner</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L5" xml:space="preserve"><value>HTTPS is enforced in production to encrypt all data in transit</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S4_L6" xml:space="preserve"><value>Soft deletes are used — when you delete a record it is flagged as deleted and excluded from queries, providing a safety net against accidental loss</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_L1" xml:space="preserve"><value>All financial records associated with your account are permanently removed</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_L2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Uploaded files and receipts are deleted from the server</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S5_L3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Account credentials are purged from the identity store</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_L1" xml:space="preserve"><value>Access — view all your financial records, account details, and uploaded documents at any time</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_L2" xml:space="preserve"><value>Correction — edit any record through the application's edit functions</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_L3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Deletion — delete any record, document, or your entire account</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_L4" xml:space="preserve"><value>Export — download your expense data as an Excel file at any time via the Export button on the Expenses page</value></data>
  <data name="Priv_S6_L5" xml:space="preserve"><value>Profile management — update your name, email, and profile photo from the Edit Profile page</value></data>
